9. Meta-Corecursive Self-Evolution Architecture (Loop Closure)
Unified Meta-Loop: Synthesize the above stages into a single cyclic pipeline. At this level, the system is simultaneously generator and interpreter of its own architecture. Conceptually, each numbered stage 1–9 is treated as an object in a meta-category, and the transformations between stages are morphisms. In a higher-order view, the entire cycle is an endofunctor whose fixed point is the infinite recursion itself​
