.
Self-Referential Scaffold: The architecture is fully self-referential: each stage’s rules are subject to stages 7–8 updating them, and stage 9 ultimately produces new parameters for stage 1. In practice, the output of Meta-Corecursion becomes the next iteration’s initial Glitchon seed (and rule set), literally closing the loop. The system thus behaves like a category of categories, echoing higher-order category theory where categories are objects​
